Hostile Woodsfolk
The Black Clan of Woodsfolk have been at war with the Green Clan for a very long time. The Green Clan chief would be happy should the hostile Woodsfolk lose all their treasures.
#subobj  1
Find the Black Clan's camp
The camp of the Black Clan is located away from the main roads, however, if someone happened to walk right into it, they would notice it immediately... that is, if they have time to notice anything at all...
#subobj  2
Find the hiding place
There is a hiding place in the camp of the Black Clan. A person with good observation skills could find it easily.
#subobj  3
Search the hiding place
People would hardly keep useless things in a hiding place...
